Filters:    
        read files
        get video from a video capture device
        decode various stream formats, such as MPEG-1 video
        pass data to the graphics or sound card
        
filter graph: a set of connected filters

filters are controlled by a high-level component called the Filter Graph Manager.
the filter graph manager provides methods for the application to build the filter graph, by connecting the filters together.


1. the application creates an instance of the filter graph manager
2. the application uses the filter graph manager to build a filter graph. the exact set of filters in the graph will depend on the applition
3.the application uses the filter graph manager to control the filter graph and stream data through the filters.

CoInitialize: initialize the COM library
CoCreateInstance: create the filter graph manager







        
